3e:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","em",null,{"children":"Sanitize markdown content for MDX compatibility using AST-aware processing.  Parses the document with remark to understand its structure, then applies targeted string replacements only to text and HTML comment nodes — code blocks, inline code, and frontmatter are automatically preserved.  Transformations applied outside code: - HTML comments to MDX comments - Curly braces in text escaped (prevents MDX expression parsing) - Angle brackets around word chars escaped (prevents JSX tag parsing)"}]}]
